<hr />
<p>UraniumEmpire made a really helpful <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/uebench">module for underrated things</a>.</p>
<hr />
<p>While I'm here, let me make something clear:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>IN THE EVENT that I am inactive from this site for five (5) years or I have died, I ask that the following stipulations be enacted:</p>
<ul>
<li>The slot for SCP-3732 is to be given to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-macleod" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1922529); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1922529&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608435330" alt="Agent MacLeod" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1922529)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-macleod" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1922529); return false;">Agent MacLeod</a></span>.</li>
<li>All of my independent works are to be given to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187885); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187885&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608435330" alt="Rounderhouse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187885)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187885); return false;">Rounderhouse</a></span></li>
<li>Collaborative works are to be attributed to the respective co-authors.</li>
</ul>
<p>ADDITIONALLY, IN THE EVENT of an EMERGENCY, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608435330" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;">Uncle Nicolini</a></span> has my phone number. Should there be a legitimate, worrying concern about my whereabouts or health, contact him.</p>
<p>THAT IS ALL.<br />
~RTME</p>
</blockquote>
<hr />
<p>Last thing, I swear. I want to tell you all how thankful I am for this community. Everyone has been so kind and patient with me and this place has affected my life in a positive way. I've been able to improve my ideas and find my creative voice through this medium, and I thank you all for the opportunity.</p>
<p><em>You better keep this a secret, friend.</em></p>
<hr /></div>
